[7] Uganda (Amuru district)
Date: Tue 3 Apr 2018
Source: NTV [edited]
http://www.ntv.co.ug/news/health/03/apr/2018/43-children-below-14-years-reported-sick-after-amuru-measles-outbreak-24802


An outbreak of measles has been reported in Amuru district with about 43 children below 14 years affected.

The District Health Officer Dr Patrict Odongo confirms the outbreak and attributes it to parents who shun immunization exercises.

